===終止任務===
M-V火箭運載的2號機及9號機原先預定發射[[LUNAR-A|LUNAR-A]]及[[破曉號|破曉號]]，前者因開發進度落後，最終取消該計畫，而後者則變更由[[H-IIA運載火箭|H-IIA運載火箭]]發射。

==接續計畫==
繼M-V運載火箭後，日本開發成本較低且能迅速裝配的固態運載火箭，稱[[艾普斯龙运载火箭|Epsilon運載火箭]]{{NoteTag|Epsilon為[[希臘字母|希臘字母]]第5個字母Ε(ε)|name=Epsilon}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jaxa.jp/projects/rockets/epsilon/index_e.html|title=Epsilon launch vehicle|accessdate=2010-04-01|publisher=JAXA|archive-date=2012-12-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DFpb9qbY?url=http://www.jaxa.jp/projects/rockets/epsilon/index_e.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，該火箭將運用[[H-IIA運載火箭|H-IIA運載火箭]]的固態輔助火箭(SRB-A)作為第一級。<ref name=asr-evolution>{{Cite document|url=http://www.senkyo.co.jp/ists2009/papers/html/pdf/2009-g-18.pdf|title=Advanced Solid Rocket Launcher and its Evolution|author=Yasuhiro Morita, Takayuki Imoto, Hiroto Habu, Hirohito Ohtsuka, Keiichi Hori, Takemasa Koreki, Apollo Fukuchi, Yasuyuki Uekusa, Ryojiro Akiba|date=2009-07-10|publisher=27th International Symposium on Space Technology and Science|accessdate=2009-09-20|postscript=<!--None-->}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref><ref name=asr-facility>{{Cite document|url=http://www.senkyo.co.jp/ists2009/papers/html/pdf/2009-g-21.pdf|title=A minimized facility concept of the Advanced Solid Rocket launch operation|author=Kazuyuki Miho, Toshiaki Hara, Satoshi.Arakawa, Yasuo Kitai, Masao Yamanishi|date=2009-07-10|publisher=27th International Symposium on Space Technology and Science|accessdate=2009-09-20|postscript=<!--None-->}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aviationweek.com/aw/generic/story_channel.jsp?channel=space&id=news/Japan111009.xml|title=New Japanese Solid Rocket On Way|publisher=[[Aviation_Week_&_Space_Technology|AVIATION WEEK]]|date=2009-11-10|accessdate=2009-12-30}}</ref>

